title: 087: Justin's Road to Ripped: Post 90 Day Update
description: Last week Justin finished his 90 day Road to Ripped challenge. His dedication paid off. He looks like a new man. You can see his results at www.mindpumpradio.com/justin. Now that the challenge is over, what is in store for him? Is he going to return to the pudgy days of yore or is he going to take it to the next level? This episode reveals all!
